@startuml
title Save/Load State Machine

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> Loading : open project
Loading --> Ready : load success
Loading --> Error : load failed

Ready --> Dirty : edit action
Dirty --> Saving : save trigger
Saving --> Ready : save success
Saving --> Error : save failed

Error --> Ready : recover/retry success
Error --> Idle : close project

Ready --> [*] : close project
Idle --> [*]

@enduml
